text: Gong Maoxin and Zhang Ze were the defending champions but chose not to defend their title. Gao Xin and Sun Fajing won the title after defeating Marc Polmans and Scott Puodziunas 2–6, 6–4, [10–7] in the final. ==Seeds== ==Draw== ==References== * Main Draw Shanghai Challenger - Doubles 2019 Doubles
